description: Response to Effects of Tropical Storm Authur

subproject.description: The proposed interventions will focus on:  a) Assisting local emergency management authorities and community organizations in the planning and preparation for the return of the affected populations to the impacted areas; b) Strengthening of the response and coordination of the UN to scale up emergency assistance and early recovery efforts during the crisis period
